snippet.title: Région Dents du Midi
snippet.description: Check out what's going on in the Région Dents du Midi and the resorts of Champéry, Les Crosets, Champoussin, Morgins and Val-d'Illiez. Welcome to the swiss side of Les Portes du Soleil area. Ski, snowboard, mountain bike and hiking paradise.
